On Thursday, the world marked girls in ICT day, which falls on the fourth Thursday of every month of April. It is marked annually as an initiative to create a global environment that empowers and encourages young women to consider studies and careers in the growing field of information and communication technologies. Here&rsquo;s Ktn&rsquo;s George Maringa with the story of four girls breaking the ultimate glass ceiling in the world of Ict.&nbsp;&nbsp;